  "texts": [
    "The dataset provides a benchmark for evaluating relation extraction models, revealing a significant performance drop when applied to financial relations, highlighting the need for more advanced models in this domain.",
    "For evaluation, we prompted the language models to output the relation of an entity pair given the list of possible relations, the entity, and the statement.",
    "The FinRED dataset is released under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0) license.",
    "The Zero-Shot prompt used for FinRED is given in Figure 13.",
    "FinRED Zero-Shot Prompt \"\"\" Classify what relationship {entity2} (the head) has to {entity1} (the tail) within the following sentence: \"{sentence}\" The relationship should match one of the following categories, where the relationship is what the head entity is to the tail entity: {\", \".join(possible_relationships)}."
